    "summary": "As Supervisor and Manager the knowledge of cross-cultural effective communication is essential. Learning how to build trust and long lasting relationships with staff, customers, suppliers, business partners is the path to a successful career  and I offer courses to achieve personal and company goals in multi-cultural environments. If you decide to relocate in Italy, the Netherlands, Czech Republic, Uruguay or Mexico, I can help you understanding the culture, finding the most effective business communication strategies so that you can avoid costly mistakes. I also offer custom-tailored Business English, Italian and Spanish courses to help you master your effective communication in the selected  language.\nI have written few Business English books, about leadership, negotiations, presentations and Italian voor Nederlanders, that you can find available on my website www.sylviabernardi.com.\nBorn in Tuscany, Italy, I began traveling and working around the world at a young age because I love learning and understanding people, solving problems, helping others grow and create situations that are a WIN-WIN for both parties.  I have worked with 48 nationalities, in three continents and in fields such as Hospitality, Sales, Customer Service, IT and Education, that is why my goal is to share knkowledge and experience to help others succeed in this global business world.",
